{"id":123434,"type":6,"name":"新絕代雙驕","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/10/73/123434_Cj4Wm.jpg","summary":"　　7０年代初，港星赴台拍戏蔚为风潮，杨盼盼、黄香莲版的[绝代双骄]就是这个时代的产物之一。似乎是受当时台湾电视风气的影响，该剧大胆 的采用了反串形式，男主角一律由女演员反串拍摄。由练武出身，在武侠剧中经常出演侠女的杨盼盼反串小鱼儿。而花无缺一角则有台湾“歌仔戏”小生黄香莲扮演。作为歌仔戏”小生，黄香莲的功架十分到位，男装扮相英气俊郎，动作潇洒大气，很有翩翩公子的风度。但该剧一众女演员，演起感情戏来，始终让人觉得有些不伦不类，以至于导致雌雄莫辨惨淡收场的结局。","info":"<li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16836\">古龍</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16549\">楊盼盼</a>、<a href=\"/person/16949\">黃香蓮</a>、<a href=\"/person/16678\">景黛音</a>、黃慧文、呂盈瑩</li><li><span>集数: </span>30</li><li><span>开始: </span>1986年</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>台灣</li><li><span>电视台: </span>台視</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"eps":[{"id":471874,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471874","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471875,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471875","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471876,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471876","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471877,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471877","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471878,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471878","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471879,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471879","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471880,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471880","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471881,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471881","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":471882,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/471882","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration